{"tid":1186750,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯：不知為什麼 兩個兒子和我不一樣 他們都是右腳球員","createTime":"2019-06-05T06:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T04:38:36.000Z","uid":54373,"like":214,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"1ae42efe02b05c29353556307ee6c8cb5aa3d2fc","tid":1186750,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/06/05/0/00f7d871dda12faad5b8fff7dce06ddc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2F0%2F00f7d871dda12faad5b8fff7dce06ddc.jpg&h=8c8e61c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美斯一家<br />\n<br />\n  美斯是巴塞的驕傲，如今他的兩個兒子泰亞高和馬特奧也都在巴塞青訓營踢球。在接受採訪時，美斯講述了自己兒子的踢球情況。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯透露：「他們二人都在球會的小學校里，起初學校為球員的孩子們組建了一個特殊小組。我們可以進去，並且可以在需要的時候帶他們出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/06/05/3/356873ab13aefa166466ce9de345a1bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2F3%2F356873ab13aefa166466ce9de345a1bd.jpg&h=3b919978&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美斯父子<br />\n<br />\n  鑒於美斯在巴塞的地位，有人笑問美斯，球會是否給了他折扣價，美斯答道：「沒有，我們和其他人一樣。泰亞高已經去了兩年了，馬特奧也去了一年了，他們都很享受。我喜歡和他們一起去球會。」<br />\n<br />\n  「泰亞高、馬特奧和我正好相反，蘇亞雷斯的兒子是左腳球員，但我的兒子卻不是。」"},{"pid":"714d501d82fac92585a7fb9078dcde331aaf5d30","tid":1186750,"uid":217374,"like":199,"dislike":1,"score":198,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7b1ee76b7724dfd1d4bd03fd90459bafff2a3b","tid":1186750,"uid":19126,"like":254,"dislike":1,"score":253,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"「泰亞高、馬特奧和我正好相反，蘇亞雷斯的兒子是左腳球員，但我的兒子卻不是。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e218e0fe91e20b2d8c401b89a5af0668703a9487","tid":1186750,"uid":8968,"like":83,"d